      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Devlog Week 7: Deployment, CI/CD &amp;amp; Running It For Real&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;devlog-week-7-deployment-cicd--running-it-for-real&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#devlog-week-7-deployment-cicd--running-it-for-real&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This week was all about getting the project out of my IDE and onto an actual server.&#xA;The goal wasn’t to add new domain features — it was to make the API build, ship, and update automatically.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
